metadata.description:
"Look Fast" is the intro track to my latest EP "Always Less", released Oct. 7 via Friends of Friends. 

The EP represents my getting back into the swing of things amidst a creative identity crisis. Throughout the entire process, I was fighting the impulses that had been cultivated over the last few years which pulled me away from music. 

"Look Fast" is exciting to me because I found a way to develop the sound I've established while keeping it cohesive with my other music.
